  "description": "A nighttime long exposure photograph captures a vibrant cityscape illuminated by countless lights, with a dramatic fireworks display exploding above. A prominent bridge stretches across a dark body of water, its lights creating a bright, linear path towards the city. The city skyline is densely packed with buildings, appearing as a cluster of glowing structures. The fireworks are white, red, and blue, with trails radiating outwards. The foreground is dominated by dark water, creating a strong contrast with the bright urban landscape. The image evokes a sense of celebration and urban energy.",
